# Best Practices

✅ Index Primary Keys

✅ Index Foreign Keys

✅ Index WHERE columns

✅ Index JOIN columns

✅ Index ORDER BY columns

✅ Index GROUP BY columns (when appropriate)

✅ Index high-selectivity columns

✅ Monitor slow queries before creating indexes

❌ Don't index every column

❌ Avoid indexing low-cardinality columns

❌ Keep unnecessary indexes

